<body>
	<%- include('../partials/navbar', { active: 'become-a-provider' }) %>
	<section class="hero">
		<div class="hero-content">
			<div class="pure-g">
				<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-2-24"></div>
				<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-12-24 order-1-small hero-text-centered flex-for-safari">
					<h1>Boost your business with Source.</h1>
				</div>
				<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-10-24 hero-image-centered flex-for-safari">
					<img src="/assets/business/hero_image.svg" alt="A coffee shop" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="purchase-router">
		<div class="pure-g">
      <div class="pure-u-1">
        <h2 class="title-2 thin center-text">Purchase our preconfigured router</h2>
        <p>
          If you’re a business or non-profit and interested in using Source, you’ve come to the right place. We know you want to remain focused on the people you serve. Instead of making life easier, technology detracts from letting you interact with your customers. Whether you’re a coffee shop, a hotelier, or a retailer, Source can integrate directly into how you give people internet access. Our professionals take care of all the installation.
        </p>
      </div>
		</div>
		<%- include('../partials/businessImageBullet', {
			title: 'Increased store traffic',
			text: 'We direct our users to your space for free. Users that have the Source app on their phone or laptop can instantly see that you‘ve installed a router. They‘re super excited to try your new fast, free internet.',
			imageSource: '/assets/business/increased_traffic.svg',
			imageAlt: 'a graph going up and to the right',
		})%>
		<%- include('../partials/businessImageBullet', {
			title: 'Point of Sale Integration',
			text: 'While we can serve internet using a captive portal solution, we can offer a better user experience with our Point of Sale Integration. When we integrate, users are prompted to download the Source App only once. This means they can instantly log on to the internet without entering passwords over and over again or clicking through endless menus. Bottom line, your customers are happier.',
			imageSource: '/assets/business/point_of_sale.svg',
			imageAlt: 'a phone with a dollar sign on it',
		})%>
		<%- include('../partials/businessImageBullet', {
			title: 'Customer Insights',
			text: 'With a Source router installed and the Source App on their phone, we can offer you deep insights into customer behavior. This includes number of visits per customer and customer lifetime value. All of this happens automatically. Learn more about customers so you can delight them.',
			imageSource: '/assets/business/insights.svg',
			imageAlt: 'a magnifying glass',
		})%>
	</section>

	<section class="off-white-bg revenue-automatically">
		<div class="inner">
			<h2 class="title-2 thin center-text">Generate revenue automatically<h2>
			<h3>Charge for access to your Source hotspot</h3>
			<p>All Source routers are pre-equipped to accept payments. If you choose, you can charge customers for using your internet.</p>
			<h3>Utilizing excess space on computers</h3>
			<p>Our router has enough storage to run a full Ethereum node and more. If you’re a coffee shop, this just means you can generate additional steady income without lifting a finger. If you’re a developer, this should really excite you.</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<%- include('../partials/footer', { background: 'off-white' }) %>
